resources.string: Minor fixes, enabled screenshots and build for Android 11 (minimum is still Android 5). Important Notice: this app is not maintained anymore, please stop using it. See the github README.md at the above link for example ways to migrate away from OneTimePass.
TOTP code now updates properly. Removed bintray dependency, use GitHub via jitpack. Minimum Android 5.0 supported.
Final codebase touch-ups for initial public release.
Theming, cosmetics, bug-fixes and code consolidations.
Finalized package name + version code, all text is ready for translating, general cosmetic UI cleanups. New feature: import/export account data.
Fix for lock setup crashing, fix clipboard bug for Android 4.2+ and add support for normal, large, xlarge and landscape layouts.
